					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="5 Ways to Transform Your Blog and Become a Digital Influencer" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150615175205-startup-guide-microinfluencers-vlog-blogger-social-media-girl-woman-laptop.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
